title: Migration balance in Belgium 2010 to 2018
summary: This line chart has an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Migration balance, with a total of 9 data points. The chart has 4 significant trends.
The longest trend is slightly negative which exists from 2013 to 2010.
Contrarily, the next significant trend is extremely positive which exists from 2018 to 2016.
Similarly, the next significant trend is extremely positive which exists from 2015 to 2013.
Similarly, the next significant trend is moderately negative which exists from 2016 to 2015.
